CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `transaction_types` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `code` varchar(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `category` enum('income','expense') NOT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `color` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'gray',
  `isSystem` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `isActive` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `transaction_types_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

INSERT INTO `transaction_types` (`name`, `code`, `category`, `description`, `color`, `isSystem`, `isActive`) VALUES
('Revenue', 'revenue', 'income', 'Income from sales and services', 'green', true, true),
('Purchase', 'purchase', 'expense', 'Purchase of goods and materials', 'blue', true, true),
('Expense', 'expense', 'expense', 'General operational expenses', 'orange', true, true),
('COGS', 'cogs', 'expense', 'Cost of Goods Sold', 'purple', true, true),
('WACC', 'wacc', 'expense', 'Weighted Average Cost of Capital', 'pink', true, true)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `name`=`name`;
